<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="39" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,466,1732]" pageId="6" pageNumber="39">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,339,1506,1532]" pageId="6" pageNumber="39">Etymology.</emphasis>
This name of this species is based on the Latin verb 
<emphasis box="[964,1080,1507,1532]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="39">caperrare</emphasis>
, meaning to frown, and refers to the distinct wrinkles between its eyes.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
